headline: Agilent to Present at the 44th Annual J.P. Morgan Healthcare Conference
summary: SANTA CLARA, Calif., December 16, 2025--Agilent Technologies Inc. (NYSE: A) today announced that CEO Padraig McDonnell and CFO Adam Elinoff will present at the 44th Annual J.P. Morgan Healthcare Conference at 9 to 9:40 a.m. PST on Tuesday, Jan. 13, 2026.
